        "content": "## ClawQL Core Observability\n\nPanels use **native protocol** metrics from **`GET /metrics`** on **clawql-mcp-http** ([`native-protocol-prometheus.ts`](https://github.com/danielsmithdevelopment/ClawQL/blob/main/src/native-protocol-prometheus.ts)). Your Prometheus datasource must **scrape** that endpoint (see [`docs/grafana/README.md`](https://github.com/danielsmithdevelopment/ClawQL/blob/main/docs/grafana/README.md)).",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
